Commentary Text: Meredith to Pooran, out Caught by Markande!! Freebie again.. Oh brilliantly taken. Markande says he caught that clean. "I can see fingers underneath the ball" says third ump. OUT! This is a lucky wicket for Meredith, more a fielder's wicket this. Slot ball on the pads for Pooran. The left-hander flicked this and didn't get the power behind the shot. Would have smashed that for six most times but deep backward square leg dives forward, gets his hands under the ball and takes it so well.
